# Use Bun Instead of npm

Use **bun** for all JavaScript/TypeScript package management. Never use npm.

## Command equivalents

| npm | bun |
|-----|-----|
| `npm install` | `bun install` |
| `npm run <script>` | `bun run <script>` |
| `npm add <pkg>` | `bun add <pkg>` |
| `npm add -D <pkg>` | `bun add -d <pkg>` |
| `npm remove <pkg>` | `bun remove <pkg>` |
| `npx <cmd>` | `bunx <cmd>` |

## Examples

```bash
# ❌ BAD
npm install
npm run dev
npx playwright test

# ✅ GOOD
bun install
bun run dev
bunx playwright test
```
